'''Reer Guuraa''' ([[ingiriis]]: nomadic people) waa [[dad]] [[xoolo]] dhaqato ah oo inta u badan u guura kolba meesha [[cows]], [[biyo]] iyo [[dhuldaaqsiimeed]] fiican leh. 
Inta u badan bulshada [[Soomaali]]du waa reer guuraa hadba ula guura xoolaha meesha [[roob]] ka da'o. Miyiga fog ayaay u hayaamaan, nolosha dadka iyo duunyada ayaa kuxiran in reer guuraagu daaq iyo doogsin u doontaan meelaha roobku kada'ay.


